🏆Best tool made for people who want to export Facebook posts.

A brilliant export tool that allows you to quickly export Facebook posts with just one click!

🖖  KEY FEATURES:

Download FB posts with one click.

🚗 DESCRIPTION Step by Step:

1.Click the export button.

⛵️ SUPPORTED COLUMNS:
Post Id
Author Id
Author
Avatar
Author Url
Content
Comments
Post Url
Reaction Count
Shared Count
Comment Count
Posted At
Extracted At

🔎  HOW DOES IT WORK:

Using Facebook's official API to export data.
Free user can export the first 50 records.
Paid users can export without limits. Only $4.99!

🔒  USAGE POLICY

No password required.
All the data you export is processed locally, so no one knows what you download.
